---
title: Double Mumbai-Style Halloumi & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Almonds
description: This deeply rich halloumi curry is like a golden sunset. Filled to the brim with bright veggies and a sprinkling of flair from the
tomato-based sauce, we think this beaming bowl will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f4f9ea4c65e1fd73e1c714-6c3afdcd.jpeg
